rap Airport|Jose Panganiban (Larap) Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Jose Panganiban, Camarines Norte|Jose Panganiban]], [[Camarines Norte]] * RPUQ&nbsp;– [[Mindoro Airport|Vigan Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Vigan]], [[Ilocos Sur]] * RPUR (BQA)&nbsp;– [[Baler Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Baler, Aurora|Baler]], [[Aurora (province)|Aurora]] * RPUS (SFE)&nbsp;– [[San Fernando Airport (Philippines)|San Fernando Airport]]&nbsp;– [[San Fernando City, La Union|San Fernando]], [[La Union]] * RPUT (TUG)&nbsp;– [[Tuguegarao Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Tuguegarao]], [[Cagayan]] * RPUU&nbsp;– [[Bulan Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Bulan, Sorsogon|Bulan]], [[Sorsogon]] * RPUV (VRC)&nbsp;– [[Virac Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Virac, Catanduanes|Virac]], [[Catanduanes]] * RPUW (MRQ)&nbsp;– [[Marinduque Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Gasan, Marinduque|Gasan]], [[Marinduque]] * RPUX&nbsp;– [[Plaridel Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Plaridel, Bulacan|Plaridel]], [[Bulacan]] * RPUY (CYZ)&nbsp;– [[Cauayan Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Cauayan, Isabela|Cauayan]], [[Isabela (province)|Isabela]] * RPUZ&nbsp;– [[Bagabag Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Bagabag, Nueva Vizcaya|Bagabag]], [[Nueva Vizcaya]] * RPVA (TAC)&nbsp;– [[Daniel Z. Romualdez Airport|Daniel Z. Romualdez (Tacloban) Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Tacloban]] * RPVB (BCD)&nbsp;– [[New Bacolod-Silay Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Silay, Negros Occidental|Silay]], [[Negros Occidental]] * RPVC (CYP)&nbsp;– [[Calbayog Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Calbayog]], [[Samar]] * RPVD (DGT)&nbsp;– [[Sibulan Airport|Sibulan (Dumaguete) Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Sibulan]], [[Negros Oriental]] * RPVE (MPH)&nbsp;– [[Godofredo P. Ramos Airport|Godofredo P. Ramos (Caticlan) Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Malay, Aklan|Malay]], [[Aklan]] * RPVF (CRM)&nbsp;– [[Catarman National Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Catarman, Northern Samar|Catarman]], [[Northern Samar]] * RPVG&nbsp;– [[Guiuan Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Guiuan, Eastern Samar|Guiuan]], [[Eastern Samar]] * RPVH (HIL)&nbsp;– [[Hilongos Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Hilongos, Leyte|Hilongos]], [[Leyte]] * RPVI (ILO)&nbsp;– [[Iloilo International Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Cabatuan, Iloilo|Cabatuan]], [[Iloilo]] * RPVJ (MBT)&nbsp;– [[Moises R. Espinosa Airport|Moises R. Espinosa (Masbate) Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Masbate City]], [[Masbate]] * RPVK (KLO)&nbsp;– [[Kalibo Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Kalibo, Aklan|Kalibo]], [[Aklan]] * RPVL&nbsp;– [[Del Pilar Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Roxas, Palawan|Roxas]], [[Palawan]] (formerly assigned to Wasig Airport, now RPLG) * RPVM (CEB)&nbsp;– [[Mactan-Cebu International Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Lapu-Lapu City]] * RPVN&nbsp;– [[Medellin Airfield]]&nbsp;– [[Medellin, Cebu|Medellin]], [[Cebu]] * RPVO (OMC)&nbsp;– [[Ormoc Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Ormoc]] * RPVP (PPS)&nbsp;– [[Puerto Princesa International Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Puerto Princesa]] * RPVQ&nbsp;– [[Biliran Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Naval, Biliran|Naval]], [[Biliran]] * RPVR (RXS)&nbsp;– [[Roxas Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Roxas, Capiz|Roxas]], [[Capiz]] * RPVS (EUQ)&nbsp;– [[Evelio Javier Airport|Evelio Javier (Antique) Airport]]&nbsp;– [[San Jose, Antique|San Jose de Buenavista]], [[Antique (province)|Antique]] * RPVT (TAG)&nbsp;– [[Tagbilaran Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Tagbilaran]], [[Bohol]] * RPVU (TBH)&nbsp;– [[Tugdan Airport|Tugdan (Tablas/Romblon) Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Alcantara, Romblon|Alcantara]], [[Romblon]] * RPVV (USU)&nbsp;– [[Francisco Reyes Airport|Francisco Reyes (Busuanga–Coron) Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Coron, Palawan|Coron]], [[Palawan]] * RPVW&nbsp;– [[Borongan Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Borongan, Eastern Samar|Borongan]], [[Eastern Samar]] * RPVX&nbsp;– [[Dolores Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Dolores, Eastern Samar|Dolores]], [[Eastern Samar]] * RPVY&nbsp;– [[Catbalogan Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Catbalogan, Samar|Catbalogan]], [[Samar]] * RPVZ&nbsp;– [[Siquijor Airport]]&nbsp;– [[Siquijor, Siquijor|Siquijor]], [[Siquijor]] * RPXX&nbsp;– used for civilian airports and airstrips with no ICAO code yet * RPZZ&nbsp;– used for military airports and airstrips with no ICAO code yet
